When I reached the city, the papers had the news of Grandma's death on the front page. Strange! All the Profs., many students and even the hotel people knew & were like brothers. Enat, people are good deep down outside - very good, that's the human truth. If they seem otherwise, it is because of some pathetic misunderstanding of some sort. 
